---
import WidgetWrapper from '~/components/ui/WidgetWrapper.astro';
---

<WidgetWrapper id="living-lab" isDark containerClass="max-w-none py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-12 md:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] md:items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">The living laboratory</p><h2
        class="mt-5 font-heading text-4xl leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Science begins in the field.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/75">
      <p>Our farm will be a long-term research platform alongside a working regenerative farm in Devon or Dorset.</p><p
        class="mt-5"
      >
        Biological sampling, environmental sensing and real-world experimentation will build an unusually rich picture
        of how an agricultural ecosystem functions over time. Everything we learn is grounded in the realities of a
        working farm.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</WidgetWrapper>
